extends layout
block content

  div.container.pb-4
    div.box
      h4.title.is-4 FAQ
      div.card
        header.card-header
          p.card-header-title Financial disclaimer
          a#financial-disclaimer.card-header-icon
            span.icon
              i.fas.fa-angle-down(aria-hidden="true")
        div.card-content
          div(style="display:none;")#financial-disclaimer-content.content
            p No part of the content that we provide constitutes financial advice, legal advice or any other form of advice meant for your specific reliance for any purpose. 
            p Any use or reliance on our content is solely at your own risk and discretion. 
            p You should conduct your own research, review, analyse and verify our content before relying on them.
            p Trading is a highly risky activity that can lead to major losses, please therefore consult your financial advisor before making any decision.
            p No content on our Site is meant to be a solicitation or offer.
      div.card
        header.card-header
          p.card-header-title Orphans status
          a#orphans.card-header-icon
            span.icon
              i.fas.fa-angle-down(aria-hidden="true")
        div.card-content
          div(style="display:none;")#orphans-content.content
            p 
              span.has-text-weight-medium invalid
              span.pl-1 => This branch contains at least one invalid block
            p
              span.has-text-weight-medium headers-only
              span.pl-1 =>  Not all blocks for this branch are available, but the headers are valid
            p
              span.has-text-weight-medium valid-headers
              span.pl-1 =>  All blocks are available for this branch, but they were never fully validated
            p
              span.has-text-weight-medium valid-fork
              span.pl-1 =>  This branch is not part of the active chain, but is fully validated